-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">驅逐共黨 光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">AGGER 100%<br />\n要紅資一毫子都賺唔到<br />\n引發支爆</span>"},{"pid":"d8190938a94e11774df1ed0f57afa513b01582a2","tid":1619111,"uid":271051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"60166fca2a0a6608fd8f6b6c9052fa0f60bf0ea9","tid":1619111,"uid":195084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1e4102fbaebbf39910fa02ba7969bd8e6a6ce2","tid":1619111,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"866e15119590b02c4e8e484867bbda23896e5e3f","tid":1619111,"uid":61396,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:47:16.000Z","msg":"打紅商有鬼用<br />\n建制 議員 高官<br />\n<br />\n笑你哋傻仔<br />\n<br />\n兵仔打兵仔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"真係 建議你睇多啲鄭立同沉旭輝"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"現階段針對官啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"紅資一樣緊要"},{"pid":"459a82c5bfd29ace2681481c066afa97273973b7","tid":1619111,"uid":100028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"中資太撚多 打唔哂<br />\n專注打政府d野先啦"},{"pid":"4d187efc5b0f1d56dd45b076bda8143571bb8a38","tid":1619111,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:37:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a0997a67efb3527360c5d1f1acc202eb9bdd65c","tid":1619111,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"8eebfa59a0ede179370cc608e3e778cbdee449b7","tid":1619111,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c627bb70f66dc75691d52c00e7e0dba7f893acd","tid":1619111,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmo