arge;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"62b17d1e23af7f7f6fdc86baf101ae6a841fd1b6","tid":1619111,"uid":316614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b4c10e8cbedf6fbc490829aee89e252d8c35f59","tid":1619111,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"你估攬炒就係流架？你估過晒緊急法 蒙面法 辱警罪 宵禁 封連燈就可以天下太平？少年你太年輕了<br />\n<br />\n我地一直忍住唔打紅鋪 唔破壞 係因為尚對政權有一丁點希望 留你地一線 一但迫到我地絕望 我地就要你地burn with us ！<br />\n<br />\n最後 引用梁天琦 ：<br />\n對住你呢個極權 對住你呢個依附極權既人<br />\n我唔會有半點既懦弱 你要規管我地既示威集會既自由 你要做既 即管去做 睇下香港人 睇下我地依班人會點對你！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:27:13.000Z","msg":"p牌推"},{"pid":"618086e2261fe1c6e42ad6ac8ec82121ecd48608","tid":1619111,"uid":237712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭想盡快捉晒勇武，鬥長命啊唔係all in啊<br />\n<br />\n［唔係end game］快閃先可以延續落去！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1620269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1620269</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae030d708a45f02cf6e0c97b13b94bd3ce84b19c","tid":1619111,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:35:20.000Z","msg":"驅逐共黨 光復香港<br />\nhit and run 不被捕<br />\n同政府部門紅店玩遊戲"},{"pid":"654109c4aa62fc96bac56a575f536b17802ff2e0","tid":1619111,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60166fca2a0a6608fd8f6b6c9052fa0f60bf0ea9","tid":1619111,"uid":195084,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a1e4102fbaebbf39910fa02ba7969bd8e6a6ce2","tid":1619111,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"866e15119590b02c4e8e484867bbda23896e5e3f","tid":1619111,"uid":61396,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:47:16.000Z","msg":"打紅商有鬼用<br />\n建制 議員 高官<br />\n<br />\n笑你哋傻仔<br />\n<br />\n兵仔打兵仔"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"真係 建議你睇多啲鄭立同沉旭輝"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"現階段針對官啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:36:17.000Z","msg":"認同"}]}